songs.title: Im Leering
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Meek Mill]
Hey, Jahlil?! We already got "So Fly" on em!
Now, it's time to take off! Haha, Let's get it!

[Chorus: Meek Mill] (2x)
1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8
I'm so mafuckin' fly, hoe, I'm bout to levitate
Im leering, Im leering, Im leering, Im leering
Bitch, Im leering, Im leering, Im leering, Im leering

[Verse 1: Meek Mill]
Let me strike a pose, hoe, take a flick
Whole team be gettin' money, we on some shit
My stomach hurtin', haters make me sick
And, I won't fuck her twice if she can't take the dick
1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8, I'm so mafuckin' fly, hoe, I'm bout to levitate
I be gettin' money honey, Trust me, I don't ever hate
Benji after benji after benji, I'm forever straight
I got in my Louie Bag any time I wanna
Gucci crossed my mind today, so I think I'm gonna
Give em green and red stripes all on my (?)
Yellow diamonds in my Breitling, wrist shine like I'm Homer
Bummer, you leased that little hoe but I'm the owner
All that hatin' shit, I'll turn you to an organ donor
You fuck wit that "Reggie", we don't smoke that Arizona
Little hoes be tryna fuck me, I say "girl, get your diploma"

[Chorus: Meek Mill] (2x)
1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8
I'm so mafuckin' fly, hoe, I'm bout to levitate
Im leering, Im leering, Im leering, Im leering
Bitch, Im leering, Im leering, Im leering, Im leering

[Verse 2: Meek Mill]
Haters yell "MAYDAY!", everyday is payday
I just wanna be successful like my nigga Trey Day
But, nothing in this world can come for free, not even AJ
I do what I wanna do, you just do what they say
I make niggas' look bad, strap it in the book bag
School of hard knocks was in a crook class; shook ass
Actin' all hard, you know who we are
We be rock-n-rollin'; no guitars cuz we stars
Shinin', blindin', a whole nother' climate
My niggas' on the block like an offensive lineman
I don't tell them haters "I'm back", say I'm rewinding
9 on my hip for the nonsense, we mobbin'
Every hoe I fuck once, wanna fuck again
Cuz I prolly cut em, Barry Sanders rushin' in
Niggas' fuck wit us but um, we don't fuck wit them
Catch me in a car dashing like my name was fuckin' Kim
Ha!

[Chorus: Meek Mill] (2x)
1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8
I'm so mafuckin' fly, hoe, I'm bout to levitate
Im leering, Im leering, Im leering, Im leering
Bitch, Im leering, Im leering, Im leering, Im leering
